\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Incarnational piety - affective devotion. They embodied their prayer and devotion, seeking to emotionally enter into their experience of prayer. Private dramas of their hearts. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
